{"tid":2095563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中澳關係】外交衝突勸退華留學生？教育界舉牌：澳洲歡迎你","createTime":"2020-07-05T14:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T15:55:27.000Z","uid":51665,"like":11,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1db9a3505e65e6500f24596fadb4086ca59af1d1","tid":2095563,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2685000/2687111/666_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2685000%2F2687111%2F666_600.jpg&h=29b594d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2685000/2687111/UNSW_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2685000%2F2687111%2FUNSW_600.png&h=f45b4d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼中國曾向留學生和遊客發出預警，籲民眾謹慎考慮赴澳之後，澳洲有商界領袖連同多名大學高層響應網上活動，高舉表示「澳洲歡迎你」的標語，並將透過微博及微信宣傳。這場運動希望彌補澳洲對華政治動盪所造成的損害，並向潛在的遊客和學生保證澳洲的安全和熱情。<br />\n<br />\n多所高校和酒店響應活動<br />\n<br />\n多人近日在推特（Twitter）上，發布手持標語的照片，並配上「澳洲歡迎你」的主題標籤（#AustraliaWelcomesYou）。據《雪梨晨鋒報》，該活動由中國澳洲論壇協調，還涉及中國澳洲商業委員會，悉尼大學，新南威爾士大學和悉尼科技大學。大型酒店集團雅高（Accor）集團和凱悅（Hyatt）酒店集團可能會參加，墨爾本大學也被邀請加入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該活動面向中國觀眾，之後還將使用微博和微信等社交網絡傳播「澳洲歡迎你」的信息。澳洲華人論壇主席Jason Yat-Sen Li說，舉辦活動的目的是希望在政治紛爭中發出普通人的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中澳商業理事會主席奧爾森（David Olsson）表示，儘管存在政治和外交問題，他仍然相信中澳關係是牢固的。他說：「我們需要做一些工作來解決這些問題」 ，「我們不能低估社交媒體的影響。我們要走在前列」。<br />\n<br />\n自澳洲呼籲調查中國疫情，再加上近期澳洲在港區國安法上的表態，中澳關係持續緊張。中國文化和旅遊部上月曾發公告稱，受新冠肺炎疫情影響，澳洲對華人與亞裔的種族歧視言行及暴力行為明顯增加，提醒中國遊客提高安全防範意識，切勿前往澳洲旅遊。教育部亦於同月發布留學預警，提醒留學生做好風險評估，謹慎選擇赴澳洲或返回澳洲學習。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHgJ8Xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHgJ8Xa.jpg&h=6520dd2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46a1fc2a939b813c0e94f66e2d6244f789815009","tid":2095563,"uid":154486,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾大學</span>"},{"pid":"f3c633da872e33cf9652cb64c9aa46cfbd062bf3","tid":2095563,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"又想被人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8883b9570e600b941afb325bd27b4effdd5242","tid":2095563,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:19:36.000Z","msg":"大劣人畀錢就入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994414790eab7cf5f659b21aac6a1ab101f6beca","tid":2095563,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49a0517d75d34e0a0650c35721ae1e19e7f11ca","tid":2095563,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c5b4243044d13bd212ecb3edcb4558b1c72597","tid":2095563,"uid":24591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"澳大利亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33579d4247ba3c7819ceb8aa04c17d85a522d8e","tid":2095563,"uid":258285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"到時可以鬥人質越多"},{"pid":"97e112dbb3234e5d22198fb57a826787a9573858","tid":2095563,"uid":51665,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTim